title: Tito's Cantina
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. An Americanized Mexican restaurant, essentially the beginnings of a chain that cater to vegans and vegetarians (another location is in Middletown). Makes its own brand of chips, fresh salsa and canned salsa. The kitchen will replace any meaty or cheesy items with more vegetable options upon request. Spacious, large portion sizes.
